{"tid":1497582,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"幼貓食野問題","createTime":"2019-08-23T04:35:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T08:11:21.000Z","uid":115277,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"5db13f6f3e27cc3067c9ceb9ab37f215ed077113","tid":1497582,"uid":115277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:35:15.000Z","msg":"話說 我7月份係公司後街執咗隻貓B<br />\n就咁望落去唔夠一個月大左右<br />\n開咗幼貓奶粉比佢飲 但就唔飲<br />\n要人手用針筒格硬擠比佢飲<br />\n其實都唔係飲好多<br />\n加上自己要返工冇時間用針筒餵<br />\n<br />\n之後聽同事買咗KAKAYO嘅MOUSSE <br />\n佢又肯食 都食左一星期左右<br />\n事後帶咗去睇醫生 醫生話呢款只可以當零食<br />\n唔適合做主食 <br />\n<br />\n睇完醫生 <br />\n醫生建議可以買啲幼貓乾糧比佢試下<br />\n當時我隻貓B都係出咗牙仔少少<br />\n但我都係診所買咗包RC嘅幼貓糧<br />\n<br />\n我試過浸濕啲糧 但佢唔肯食<br />\n所以我買啲主食罐<br />\n試過SCHESIR ZIWIPEAK WELLNESS <br />\n佢都唔食 <br />\n唯一SCHESIR佢會肯食 但痾爛屎<br />\n之後再轉CANAGAN 佢肯食 仲要痾靚屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家想慢慢氹佢食乾糧<br />\n第二次睇醫生打針 <br />\n屎忽痕買左包RC GROWTH幼貓糧<br />\nRC 聽講多味精多油 <br />\n依家諗緊溝唔溝埋啲罐頭一齊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />請問有冇幼貓糧推介？<br />\n同埋我長期餵罐頭有冇問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7nk6MUD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7nk6MUD.jpg&h=08f98125&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AeCwX1m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAeCwX1m.jpg&h=d2574e25&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"afc2e3a7303edc0db0723907bc0331fb3d41f7e4","tid":1497582,"uid":175659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T04:38:42.000Z","msg":"長期餵主食罐冇問題，但貴，易肥，麻煩<br />\n<br />\n睇完都覺得你果隻第日會揀飲擇食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53c77f878c6f155e2245cbe1d98fd781ed741292","tid":1497582,"uid":115277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"afc2e3a7303edc0db0723907bc0331fb3d